00:30:07.272 --> 00:30:08.480
AUDIENCE: And one more thing.

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:11.879
Why is the gs 0?

00:30:11.879 --> 00:30:12.420
HONG LIU: No.

00:30:12.420 --> 00:30:16.290
This is the surface
