00:31:02.590 --> 00:31:03.670
And so you have a string.

00:31:03.670 --> 00:31:04.920
Then you go around the circle.

00:31:04.920 --> 00:31:05.950
This is one loop.

00:31:09.840 --> 00:31:14.960
And indeed, when you
