00:58:01.700 --> 00:58:04.260
then that means the
modes, the dynamics

00:58:04.260 --> 00:58:07.130
control the location
of the D-brane

00:58:07.130 --> 00:58:10.805
must not have any potential,
can only have derivative terms.

00:58:14.470 --> 00:58:17.390
