01:06:50.510 --> 01:06:53.420
When you put together,
from conventional wisdom,

01:06:53.420 --> 01:06:55.290
you say, maybe I just
have two Maxwell.

01:06:57.890 --> 01:06:59.850
From conventional
wisdom, you two Maxwell.

